Package com.example.androidapp

This application was designed to search for canteens of Charles University. User can set searching parameters like minimal rating of the university or maximal distance. Canteens that suits to searching parameters are shown to user. Canteens are shown one by one and user can switch between them. Order of the canteens is based on the sorting option which is set. Application provides 3 searching options, by: alphabet, rating and distance. User can see details about canteen like its name, rating, distance or opening time. User can also can visit canteen website to watch its menu or to find route to the canteen.
